Cell["\<\
Figure 4.1  Theophylline Subject 1: the 11 measurements (points) with the 90% \
posterior-predictive concentration band from the fitted two-compartment \
model. The model captures the absorption peak near 2 h and the slow \
elimination tail; the data fall inside the band.\
\>", "Text",
 CellMargins->{{70, 70}, {2, 14}},
 FontSize->11,
 FontSlant->Italic,
 FontColor->GrayLevel[
  0.35],ExpressionUUID->"7037b7d2-c82a-450a-850b-89c2de7da0da"],

Cell["\<\
The posterior marginals (a Sobol\[CloseCurlyQuote] draw from the Laplace \
posterior) show what the 11 points do and do not pin down:\
\>", "Text",
 CellMargins->{{50, 50}, {6, 
  6}},ExpressionUUID->"e97891ba-b9ca-41c3-b3e8-008c864700e3"],

